# RFC 8288 Link response headers for agent / machine discovery.
# A single source honored by BOTH deploy targets: Astro copies this file from
# public/ into the published output (dist/client for the Cloudflare adapter,
# dist root for the Netlify adapter), and each platform's static asset handler
# applies it. Keep this as the only place these headers are defined so the two
# targets never drift.
# Relation types are IANA-registered and point to resources that exist:
#   describedby -> /llms.txt   (LLM-readable description of this site, RFC 8288)
#   service-doc -> /docs       (human-oriented documentation, RFC 8631)
/*
  Link: </llms.txt>; rel="describedby"; type="text/plain", </docs>; rel="service-doc"; type="text/html"
